# Product Catalog Conventions

Apply these rules automatically to every new product added to `products` in `src/lib/data.ts` — don't wait to be asked again.

## Title (naming)

Format: `"[Имя] — [тип/форма сумки]"` (no color in the title — color is shown separately via the `colors` swatch UI).

- One unique, premium-sounding first name per product (Italian/French feminine names, Italian/French place names, soft nature words). No repeats across the catalog.
- Never use real luxury brand names (Gucci, Prada, Celine, Dior, Chanel, Hermès, Jacquemus, Furla, Guess, etc.).
- Never reuse the catalog's own sub-brand names as a product name: `luma-atelier`/SÓRA Atelier, `aurelia`, `marrone`, `castello`, `vionetta`, `pelle-nova`.
- Avoid cheap-sounding titles ("Сумка женская 2025", "Модная сумочка", "Люкс сумка").
